case_circumstances: Decomposed body of a young woman was found by Tohono O'odham PD on the rear porch of an abandoned house.  Also discovered was a man's body in the front of the house in a similar state of decomposition.  This man was later identified as an undocumented migrant from Huetenanango, Guatemala (Agusto Miguel Juan).
